Monet_1906_Water_Lilies.jpg,Monet,Claude Monet,1840–1926,Water Lilies,1906,Oil on canvas,One of Monet's most celebrated series depicting the water garden at his estate in Giverny. **Water Lilies** was painted late in his life as his eyesight was failing.
